                         |7 Wonders - Treasures of Seven|
                         +------------------------------+

+----------------+
|Game Description|
+----------------+

Build nine of the most intriguing structures throughout history in this innovative match-3 game. Make matches and clear runes to reveal ancient secrets as you puzzle your way into the hidden City of the Gods!

+----------------------------------+
|Instructions / System Requirements|
+----------------------------------+

No install or crack is required for this portable version. Extract the ZIP file and create a shortcut to the executable (EXE) to play.

- Windows XP/Vista

- Pentium III 1GHz Processor

- 256MB RAM

- DirectX 8.1 or higher

- DirectX Compatible 16 or 32-bit Video Card with 64MB VRAM

- DirectSound-compatible sound card

